race.comment: TJAKA (4) gets a much better set-up for this with the 3kg claim at his second run back. Drifted back from the inside draw and didn't do much when sixth over 1100m at Goulburn. Smart when right and suited out to the 1425m. REVOKE (11) seven-start Maiden with his hoof on the till. Raced a little closer from the inside gate when a surprise third over 1650m at this track. In peak condition and can surprise here. MYSTIC DIVA (6) chipped away late after giving them a big start when fourth over 1300m at this track. Gets a better set-up and stays in the mix. JAMARNI (2) only the one win from seventeen starts and is quickly running out of chances. Kept safe in betting when he failed to close off to finish eighth over 1425m at this track. Take on trust.
